VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT amsiInitFailed|AmsiScanBuffer|amsi\.dll|amsiContext|Disable.*AMSI|AMSI.*bypass
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:amsi|AmsiScanBuffer|amsiContext|amsiInitFailed && MISSING:test|development|example|research
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects known patterns associated with Antimalware Scan Interface (AMSI) bypass techniques.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for AMSI Bypass Attempt.
